        "type": "code",
        "value": "import numpy as np\nfrom scipy.stats import special_ortho_group\nx = special_ortho_group.rvs(3)"
      },
      {
        "type": "code",
        "value": "np.dot(x, x.T)"
      },
      {
        "type": "code",
        "value": "import scipy.linalg\nscipy.linalg.det(x)"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "value": "This generates one random matrix from SO(3). It is orthogonal and\nhas a determinant of 1."
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "value": "Alternatively, the object may be called (as a function) to fix the `dim`\nparameter, returning a \"frozen\" special_ortho_group random variable:"
      },
      {
        "type": "code",
        "value": "rv = special_ortho_group(5)\n# Frozen object with the same methods but holding the\n# dimension parameter fixed."
